WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.146 --> 00:00:04.946
Hapihapitchi Is Popular?!

00:00:06.646 --> 00:00:07.916
Morning!

00:00:07.946 --> 00:00:10.086
Wake up, everyone!

00:00:12.286 --> 00:00:13.486
Morning.

00:00:13.516 --> 00:00:16.146
Hi, Hapihapitchi.

00:00:17.016 --> 00:00:19.616
Hi, Mametchi, Chamametchi!

00:00:21.746 --> 00:00:23.786
Morning, Mamametchi.

00:00:23.816 --> 00:00:26.986
Hapihapitchi, thanks
for your help.

00:00:29.216 --> 00:00:32.786
It's time to wake up!

00:00:33.116 --> 00:00:36.686
I was working till late
last night.

00:00:37.246 --> 00:00:41.686
You will be late for work,
Papamametchi.

00:00:43.916 --> 00:00:46.416
Leave it to Hapihapitchi!

00:00:47.086 --> 00:00:50.846
Hapihapi. Hapihapi!

00:00:53.016 --> 00:00:56.416
Yeah! I'll work hard today!

00:00:58.646 --> 00:01:01.246
You have a test today.

00:01:01.586 --> 00:01:03.216
What!!??

00:01:03.546 --> 00:01:05.116
I'll do my best!

00:01:05.186 --> 00:01:09.016
It's easy for you to say.
You're smart.

00:01:09.046 --> 00:01:11.086
I'll fail-tchi.

00:01:12.086 --> 00:01:13.116
Here we go.

00:01:13.286 --> 00:01:15.846
Hapihapi!

00:01:22.616 --> 00:01:26.016
I hate tests, but
I'll try my best!

00:01:26.086 --> 00:01:28.216
Me too-tchi.

00:01:28.286 --> 00:01:29.686
Yay!

00:01:31.516 --> 00:01:34.486
You guys are great!

00:01:34.646 --> 00:01:35.586
Okay...

00:01:38.816 --> 00:01:41.546
You get a "Great Award"!

00:01:43.786 --> 00:01:44.746
Yay!

00:01:54.786 --> 00:01:56.646
Hello, Hapihapitchi.

00:01:56.686 --> 00:01:57.716
Hello.

00:01:57.746 --> 00:02:00.816
It's so nice to see you!

00:02:01.016 --> 00:02:02.916
Hapihapi.

00:02:03.046 --> 00:02:05.716
Please come by sometime.

00:02:06.416 --> 00:02:07.546
I will!

00:02:09.316 --> 00:02:10.746
A butterfly!

00:02:14.386 --> 00:02:17.546
Why is Hapihapitchi so popular?

00:02:17.916 --> 00:02:19.246
Because...

00:02:19.586 --> 00:02:21.716
Hapihapi Happy!

00:02:26.746 --> 00:02:32.116
Hapihapitchi has a special
power to make people happy.

00:02:32.216 --> 00:02:33.216
Yes-tchi!

00:02:34.146 --> 00:02:37.286
Be happy, Hapi!

